# 16-Channel Relay Control Board

## Overview

This project showcases a custom **2-layer PCB** designed in **KiCad** for a 16-channel relay control system used in an industrial helmet cleaning application.

The PCB was developed to provide reliable switching of multiple high-power loads through relay outputs while maintaining compact component placement and organized signal routing. It interfaces with a microcontroller for automated control of cleaning system components.

---

## Features

- 2-Layer PCB Design
- 16 Relay Output Channels
- Microcontroller Interface
- High-Current Relay Driver Circuitry
- Power Distribution Network
- Screw Terminal Connectors
- Modular Connector Layout
- Compact PCB Design
- 3D Mechanical Model (STEP)

